Revision history for Net-Async-Hetzner

0.003     2026-02-12 17:23:03Z
    - Initial release
    - Net::Async::Hetzner::Cloud - async Cloud API client
    - Net::Async::Hetzner::Robot - async Robot API client
    - IO::Async integration via IO::Async::Notifier
    - Future-based async HTTP methods (get, post, put, delete)
    - Reuses WWW::Hetzner _build_request/_parse_response for request/response logic
    - Net::Async::HTTP for non-blocking transport
    - Basic Auth support for Robot API
